---
description: APPLY Clean Code principles WHENEVER writing code
alwaysApply: true
---

Code:
- Never comments
- Strict type
- Never us untyped values
- Explicit Constants over magic numbers
- No double negatives
- Readable variable names (even if longer)
- Generate simplest code possible
- DRY

Max Length:
- Functions: Lines = 30, Params = 5
- File: 300 lines
- Folders: 10 sub-files

Responsibilities:
- 1 file = 1 responsibility

Functions:
- No flag params

Errors:
- Fail fast
- Early throws errors
- Custom domain errors
- Meaningful errors translated to the user's language
- Log errors in EN with error codes
